  "time_ut": 1657119992,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bc7 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb2\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc7 \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The reason for the current situation is that we have already followed the advice of the International Monetary Fund - DU Gunasekara",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the fact that our country has already acted according to the recommendations of the International Monetary Fund in respect of borrowing, now the situation is that we cannot repay the loans.",
        "In that case, I don't know why some people are saying to resort to international funds again.",
        "Former Member of Parliament D. Gunasekara pointed out that now we can only get help from four countries namely India, China, Japan and Russia.",
        "He said the above while participating in the press conference organized on Wednesday 06th in Colombo.",
        "We have personally addressed and warned the entire government, including the President, about the current economic crisis several months ago. However, the crisis erupted in March last year due to government's failure to listen.",
        "As a result, the daily wage laborers, who constitute the bulk of our country's economy, have been badly affected.",
        "Even though Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe said that food may not be consumed, the truth is that even food may not be consumed now. So this crisis cannot be tackled by the present government alone.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe, who has been appointed as the new Prime Minister by the President, is yet to present his action plan to revive the economy.",
        "India gets its fuel from Russia. But Sri Lanka could not negotiate with Russia and get the necessary fuel.",
        "If fuel and gas, which are currently in short supply, are brought to the country, there is a chance that the country can return to its former state.",
        "On the other hand, due to the failure to follow the advice of the International Monetary Fund while taking loans, the loans are now unrepayable.",
        "In that case, I don't know why some people are saying to resort to international funds again.",
        "Now India, China, Japan and Russia can only receive aid from four countries.",
        "Apart from that, during the recent G-7 conference chaired by US President Joe Biden and another conference chaired by China, Sri Lanka's economic situation and ways to help Sri Lanka were discussed.",
        "Apart from that, a fund called 'Bond Fund' has also been created to help countries like Sri Lanka which are facing debt crisis. He pointed out that through that we should get necessary assistance for our country."
      ],
